[DQC.IFRS.0105.9556] The following elements are in the presentation linkbase of [00020] - Statement - Financial Position but are not included in any calculation relationship in the filing. LEG:CurrentBorrowingsAndCurrentPortionOfNonCurrentBorrowingsOtherThanThoseSpecificallyRelatedToBankingAndInsuranceActivities, ifrs-full:ProvisionsForEmployeeBenefits, ifrs-full:LiabilitiesIncludedInDisposalGroupsClassifiedAsHeldForSale, ifrs-full:OtherShorttermProvisions, ifrs-full:DeferredTaxLiabilities, ifrs-full:TradeAndOtherCurrentPayables, ifrs-full:CurrentProvisionsForEmployeeBenefits, ifrs-full:LeaseLiabilities, ifrs-full:OtherCurrentLiabilities, ifrs-full:CurrentTaxLiabilitiesCurrent, ifrs-full:TradeAndOtherPayables, LEG:BorrowingsOtherThanThoseSpecificallyRelatedToBankingAndInsuranceActivities, ifrs-full:OtherProvisions, ifrs-full:CurrentLeaseLiabilities All elements appearing in the face of the financial statements should be included in a calculation relationship somewhere in the filing.
